description: The Windsor wall mount mailbox offers small capacity solutions for average mail deliveries. The mailbox is made from polypropylene plastic, that will never rust. The simple, elegant and powerful, deeply embossed design on the front of the Windsor mailbox replicates the appearance of royalty.
